352
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:28,280
If this is thoroughly investigated,
will you remain innocent?

353
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:29,920
This trick of Mo Shenhai's

354
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,840
is meant to drag
all of us down with him.

355
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:34,720
How could you be so reckless?

356
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:42,400
Mo Shenhai is making
his last-ditch effort

357
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:45,680
because he's failed to beat me.

358
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,320
And you've witnessed

359
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:48,680
how strong my bodyguards are.

360
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:50,680
He can't lay a finger on me.

361
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:53,720
If the two biggest companies
in Mo City fall,

362
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,360
your position

363
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:56,960
will be gone too.

364
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,880
By then,

365
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,800
apart from us two,

366
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,660
