369
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,200
Timing beats all.

370
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,480
Take your time with the investigation.

371
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:13,560
Naturally, I won't forget your kindness.

372
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:17,680
The Hu family happens to have
some properties in your hometown.

373
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:22,280
Let that be a gift for your two sons
and daughter back home.

374
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:25,240
This case

375
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:27,120
